tika.dc.description: Boys and girls' bodies are the same in some ways and different in others. Everybody Has a Body: God Made Boys and Girls discusses the differences between male and female bodies in a way that children aged 2-5 can understand. The book introduces children to the way gender contributes to the dignity of the human person. Everybody Has a Body is a simple, fun introduction to the differences between boys and girls.
